headline.main: Iraq Welcomes Removal From Revised US Travel Ban
headline.print_headline: Iraq Welcomes Removal From Revised US Travel Ban

lead_paragraph: Iraq welcomed its removal from a revised U.S. travel ban on Monday, calling it a "positive message" at a time when American and Iraqi forces are battling the Islamic State group.
